1. Sibling project: Aozora Flavored Markdown (Apache-2.0 OR MIT)
================================================================================

aozora-flavored-markdown-epub depends on the `aozora-flavored-markdown`
library crates (`aozora-flavored-markdown`, `aozora-encoding`) consumed
from crates.io as semver deps, to convert
Aozora Flavored Markdown sources into the XHTML fragments that EPUB3
spine items embed. Aozora Flavored Markdown itself is dual-licensed under Apache-2.0 OR MIT
and ships its own NOTICE file naming the upstream comrak fork and the
CommonMark / GFM / Aozora Bunko material it incorporates. Refer to
https://github.com/P4suta/aozora-flavored-markdown/blob/main/NOTICE for the authoritative
chain.


